Package uk.co.listing

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseIntegrationTest
    Base class for JUnit tests which are expected to do end to end integration tests (using real appContext configurations) This does not roll back transactions Also you can add your other app-context and test specific configuration files here in @ContextConfiguration
    BaseMockingUnitTest
    Base class for normal JUnit tests that are expected to be mocking objects.
    BaseTransactionalIntegrationTest
    Base class for JUnit tests which are expected to clean up after themselves like Database tests and other integration tests.
    ListingTestUtils  
    RunCukesGroupOneIT
    This will run all your cucumber features and steps tagged with @groupone
    RunCukesGroupTwoIT
    This will run all your cucumber features and steps tagged with @grouptwo
    SeleniumConnector
    Base class to inherit the cucumber steps from, which will drive the selenium tests
